# Testing Rules

Prefer Vitest (unit) + Playwright (e2e).

## Must cover when touched

- Checkout/payment webhook duplicate delivery
- Inventory reserve/release
- Illegal order/article/campaign transitions
- AuthZ denial cases
- Medical publish gate
- Campaign payment release gate

## Practices

Deterministic tests (fake clocks/network). New bug ⇒ regression test when feasible. Do not disable tests to greenwash. Critical journeys: checkout, publish, reverse-bid award.
